---
// ProfileCard.astro - 简洁风格
---

<aside class="sticky top-24 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
  <!-- 头像 -->
  <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-4 bg-gray-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
    <span class="text-4xl text-gray-400">👤</span>
  </div>
  
  <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900 text-center">
    Huggin
  </h2>
  
  <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-4 text-center">
    Developer • Tech Explorer
  </p>
  
  <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-4 mb-4">
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
      欢迎来到我的博客，这里记录着我的技术探索和生活点滴。
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <!-- 社交链接 -->
  <div class="mt-4 flex justify-center space-x-4">
    <a href="https://github.com/Huggin423" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600 transition-colors" title="GitHub">
      <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
